Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:30.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.33,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after\NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves\N caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country will soon be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it will be rebuilt under a new king.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namely, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Citizens of Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to say goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the old Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours from now, at Conchcorde Plaza,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to cut this \Nincompetent King's head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you are somewhere on \Nthe island watching this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people shattered Arlong's dream \N- he was a symbol of Fish-Men's anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Usopp! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What fools...\N--I can't believe they got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's water!\N--It's water!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That room will be filled with water by \Nthe time we finish executing the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lowly creatures can't\N survive that, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark! Take me to the Ryugu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Wait," Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people shouldn't fight Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei! They have my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I got to do something about Hordy \Nbefore my friends get into real trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't let my guard down \Njust because we fought together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost forgot that \Nyou're that man's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ready to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:29.43,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"A Rift Opens Up!\NLuffy vs. Jimbei!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People called me The Submarine \Nof the East Blue when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can easily swim even an 82-foot pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can run that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't swim but I can run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook! Let's see which one \Nof us is faster sometime soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat me! I'm going \Nto run beyond the horizon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it doesn't look good, does it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't! The surface of \Nthe water is getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Look, look! The water is...\N--It's coming! It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?! \NHow can you be so calm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Do you have any ideas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't be so honest!\N--That's so clear, I like it. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it in front of you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is "it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dorororororo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone, bone, bone, bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Brook, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone, bone, bone, bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, w-wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got some explaining to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do something like that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can make my soul leave my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like a real dead person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened when I was on \Nmy world tour as Soul King...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in quite a slump \Nat that time for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.43,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}TDS SALES PLUMMET----\NCONCERT TICKETS REMAIN UNSOLD
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sales of TDs and concert \Ntickets were dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's concert was not so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not making great music lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't feel his soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you, Brook?\N Write a new song that will sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy to make a hit song...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Music is something much more sublime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... Maybe, the God of Music\N doesn't love me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time... Just one more song is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God! God of Music!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bless me with a melody that will \Nshake everybody to their soul! God!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:09:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I got this ability, \NI noticed what's missing in my songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a way out of my slump!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What was it?\N--Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had the ability to pass\N undetected through walls...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any able-bodied male \Nunderstands the potential, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous, Zoro! I wish I were him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the water got that high!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin! Boss Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Jimbei! Hold on a second!\N What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to the Ryugu Palace to save\N my crew and kick that Hordy guy's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Don't do it"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, why do you have to fight now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama! Boss Jimbei-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark! Take me! To the Ryugu Place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Wait"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish-Man Karate--Shark Brick Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked?! He's supposed to be immune\N to blows like that as a rubber man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fish-Man Karate is all about \Nmanipulating the water around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shock wave can travel \Nthrough water vapor in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and through to the water \Nwithin your target's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every living thing is made up of water. \NSo even a rubber man can't escape the impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Stamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all you learned from your training?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bet on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, move aside, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:12:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the reason but \Nyou two are friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why did Robin come out of the forest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:31.89,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}WATERWHEEL TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just give up! You guys can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Didn't you see \NBoss Hordy's broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country will be destroyed.\N And Neptune is gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do so, you'll be no better than them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuboshi, Manboshi, take them into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I got it-so-la-ti-do!\N--Count on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as indulgent as before-dosun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does indulgence run in the\N Neptune family's blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not just getting back at \Nhumans but hurting your fellow beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it pain your heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any Fish-Man who sides with \Nhumans deserves death-dosun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lead the way for your \Nfather--towards death! Fukaboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got the New Fish-Man Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the 3 great royal brothers could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Fukaboshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to Conchcorde \NPlaza to save our father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go to the execution ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want some of us to \Nstay here at the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Hordy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Ryugu Palace is impregnable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave some men to open the\N gate when we come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want the new \Nking getting locked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be nonsense-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't win citizens'\N hearts with violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have only a little \Nlife left. Say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid swordsman cut me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drug is wearing off.\NHey, give me the Energy Steroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to take that much at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, what should we do \Nabout those 3 Straw Hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just humans. \NThey'll drown if we leave them like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who is coming to save them,\N no one can break into the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, how are the new residents\N from the Fish-Man District doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're already moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. \NThere'll be empty houses for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some will leave the country\N and the others will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can just move into those houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make a great country in which \Nall citizens can look down on humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it! The ray of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Fish-Men that we saw earlier are \Nall gone and nobody is here in the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they left Pappagu-san behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:17:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, Brook, \Nask Pappagu to find the key to unchain us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And the keys to this cage and this room...\N--Wait a minute, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my swords is enough.\N Just bring my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're so reliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll go ask Pappagu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? I thought we \Nwere just invited to a banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if those Straw Hats are doing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pappagu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pappagu-san...\N--What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ghost--I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pappagu-san! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much time! I need the\N key... I mean, the sword! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!!\N--What do you mean "No"? Listen to me! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, you two? And Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen if you guys resort to \Nviolence now on the Fish-Man Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everytime Fish-Men tried to open their \Nhearts to humans, humans disappointed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Humans are very violent."\N "Humans hate and look down on Fish-Men."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened in the past planted those\N twisted ideas in Fish-Men's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the case of Arlong,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,many Fish-Men believe that humans \Nhunted him because he was a Fish-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you, the people who beat\N Arlong, fight Hordy now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what do you think will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it helps the island\N overcome this crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,witnessing you people knocking down \NHordy who is standing against humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would make the islanders to think\N that things will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Jimbei,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to rescue our crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if nothing is done, \NHordy will rule the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have so many friends on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been trying so hard \Nto hide who did that to you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you said a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that Hordy attacks those Fish-Men\N who are sympathetic to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get beaten by them \Nbecause you spoke up for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin, is that true? \NHordy and his crew did that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think part of the reason Luffy wants \Nto fight is because this is your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you helped our captain \Nwhen he had his back against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't thank you enough for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Luffy wants to fight,\N we will go along with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just leave the island like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have reason to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie-chan's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Shirahoshi-chan's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! This country is the \NMermaid paradise of my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way, Jimbei! \NYou gotta let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.42,0:22:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't! Leave it up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.93,0:22:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just beat my way past you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight you as many times as \NI have to till you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neptune's execution draws ever closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.38,0:23:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy's powerful allies are mobilizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New Fish-Man Pirates are overrunning \Nevery part of Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.39,0:23:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, just as his ambition \Nis coming to fruition,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an terrifying change befalls Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Something Has Happened to Hordy!\N The True Power of the Evil Drug!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
